                    <li>Kids can indulge in fun excursions like snorkelling, wildlife watching, or discovering trails in Mother Nature, while parents may indulge in spa treatments, sunset views, or romantic dinners for two. Fresh and creative island resorts generally offer family activities for kids’ fun while you relax. </li>
                    <li>So sit on the sandy beach, visit hidden coves, and enjoy the cooking of the island itself; if you are not into this, you should think twice. It is appropriate for family members to bond while enjoying the luxury of intimacy that only an island paradise can offer.</li>
                </ul>

