                    <li>Parents might choose to unwind in the spa, eat at gourmet restaurants, or lounge at private pools, whereas the children enjoy supervised kids’ clubs, waterparks, and activities suitable for their interests. Such family-friendly resorts also have programs like art classes, adventure camps, or educational nature walks, which allow kids to have fun just as much as their parents do. </li>
